rmal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"762642aef8e323969953a7e17c4271282f272ff4","tid":1765944,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:51:31.000Z","msg":"橫掂都係<br />\n其實應該再辣D<br />\n要入紙取締條惡法"},{"pid":"b88c6038d1c8b2230fdbb9fdb76cb8019cdcb67e","tid":1765944,"uid":156913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:52:32.000Z","msg":"直接告班狗非法集結啦，佢地出黎咪破壞社會安寧囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65448e80ea2c2117692bb965160e2fdd4865aa3","tid":1765944,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:52:44.000Z","msg":"直接告班狗非法集結啦，佢地出黎咪破壞社會安寧囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9aeff721c2f04e94a0e284d0fc308a5d8151ca2","tid":1765944,"uid":104865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:05:47.000Z","msg":"立法會議員區諾軒和朱凱廸提出私人草案，建議修改《公安條例》第18條及19條，有關「非法集結罪」及「暴動罪」的控罪定義及最高刑期。<br />\n<br />\n前立法會議員吳靄儀表示，現行《公安條例》定義太廣泛，令警方能大規模拘捕，違反人權。她認為，若草案能提交立法會討論，政府就應該暫時停止檢控，待控罪門檻被清晰定義後，才繼續控告被捕人士。<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒補充，現行《公安條例》過時，修改是當務之急，國際間曾多次批評條例定義狹窄，行政長官若拒絕批出修訂許可，將在國際間換來更大壓力。"},{"pid":"56b86c2cfec754ac2c06f03dafb7ec8bbc921d97","tid":1765944,"uid":183538,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:35:21.000Z","msg":"下 姐係我地要支持義士俾人入暴動罪架？"},{"pid":"96ef2af93d29b1da469070a61fbeb58ffb2999c7","tid":1765944,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:36:01.000Z","msg":"全民議政 監察 由like 388個區議員fb做起<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1765994\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1765994</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"085e98b6e92e2930abb1cc4069ae43866a4f52f6","tid":1765944,"uid":95577,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"56b86c2cfec754ac2c06f03dafb7ec8bbc921d97","tid":1765944,"uid":183538,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTim